At the same time, she lost something that has always been her capital in the competition for rich clients: the sanctity of discretion.
After this scandal, the Swiss banking secret was no longer what it used to be.
This was followed by the resignation of the Chairman of the Board of Directors and the Chairman of the Board of Directors.
And the exodus of customers' money.
